Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of a neural network trained using genetic algorithm for implementing an intelligent sensory system for gas detection. This involves concepts from artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). The use of genetic algorithm also falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the implementation of the system, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SY).
